WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:01.600
Right

00:03.360 --> 00:04.120
My father

00:04.920 --> 00:05.920
Has more words for you

00:07.040 --> 00:07.920
Yue'er

00:09.040 --> 00:10.320
I'm afraid

00:11.000 --> 00:13.000
I won't live to see Your Highness

00:14.120 --> 00:14.680
Father

00:20.360 --> 00:22.480
Tell Your Highness for me

00:23.040 --> 00:24.680
This northern expedition

00:25.360 --> 00:27.320
Could not press on

00:27.560 --> 00:29.360
To reclaim the land

00:30.440 --> 00:31.720
Then we should

00:32.560 --> 00:35.040
Follow my original plan

00:35.880 --> 00:38.480
Use Beiyu Pass as a springboard

00:39.040 --> 00:40.560
Actively prepare

00:41.360 --> 00:43.360
And wait for the right time

00:43.920 --> 00:44.800
Yue'er

00:45.920 --> 00:47.680
I have something

00:48.800 --> 00:50.800
To give to Your Highness

00:52.040 --> 00:53.800
General Zu Kun has something to give me

01:23.040 --> 01:23.560
This

01:24.800 --> 01:26.880
Is soil from less than two hundred li from Yong'an

01:27.480 --> 01:28.480
Please take it back, Your Highness

01:28.920 --> 01:29.720
Let the court's

01:29.720 --> 01:30.680
Nobles

01:31.720 --> 01:32.920
Take a good look at this homeland

01:33.360 --> 01:33.920
The court

01:33.920 --> 01:35.800
The court has its own considerations

01:36.360 --> 01:37.800
Has difficulties and hardships

01:38.120 --> 01:38.920
Various concerns

01:39.680 --> 01:40.320
I know

01:44.120 --> 01:45.480
Heaven did not grant more years

01:46.560 --> 01:48.120
Only leaving endless regret

01:56.360 --> 01:57.800
Brothers of the volunteer army

01:58.720 --> 01:59.920
The war is over

02:00.240 --> 02:01.560
I will arrange places for you

02:01.800 --> 02:02.720
Those willing to take up arms

02:02.880 --> 02:03.680
Will join the army

02:04.240 --> 02:05.120
Those willing to take money

02:05.480 --> 02:07.360
I will send people to take you to Liangzhou

02:34.040 --> 02:35.120
I'll follow Your Highness

02:37.480 --> 02:38.560
Follow Your Highness

02:38.560 --> 02:44.120
Follow Your Highness

02:44.120 --> 02:44.600
Good

02:44.600 --> 02:45.480
Follow Your Highness

02:46.120 --> 02:47.040
From today

02:47.360 --> 02:49.320
I will form you into a separate army

02:49.920 --> 02:51.120
Led by General Zhu

02:51.560 --> 02:52.040
Yes

02:52.120 --> 02:53.120
Since this army

02:53.800 --> 02:54.920
Was built in the north

02:55.240 --> 02:56.440
I give you the name

02:57.000 --> 02:58.000
Beishuo Army

03:00.320 --> 03:01.440
Beishuo Army

03:01.560 --> 03:02.600
At your command

03:03.360 --> 03:04.320
Here

03:09.040 --> 03:09.600
Brother-in-law

03:10.240 --> 03:10.920
Urgent edict from the Ministry of War

03:22.000 --> 03:22.560
What is it?

03:22.920 --> 03:23.800
Father is gravely ill

03:24.040 --> 03:25.040
Summoning me to return to the capital immediately

03:25.360 --> 03:26.240
At this time

03:27.480 --> 03:28.680
Go investigate the situation again

03:29.600 --> 03:31.120
Call Zhu Yuanzhi to discuss together

03:32.040 --> 03:32.560
Yes

03:48.800 --> 03:49.680
All investigated
